      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD boundary conditions shown to be equivalent to experimental test conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "CFD inlet flow rates and impeller speeds were set to match experimentally measured values within ±0.5% and ±10 RPM respectively. Blood viscosity in the CFD model was set to the experimentally measured value at 37°C. Equivalency between CFD inputs and experimental conditions is judged adequate for MRL 2."
    }
